description:
Danny aims to take your mind off your troubles with a Hoda detour, plus a few words on Real Housewives of Atlanta. Danny also plays a portion of his live show chats with Cary and Mark Deuber from The Real Housewives of Dallas, and Mark Cuevas from Love Is Blind on Netflix.


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
